  <brief_title>Monitoring of Anaesthesic Depth in the Cerebral Cortex Using Bispectral Bilateral System.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Monitoring of Anaesthetic Depth at Different Locations in the Cerebral Cortex Using Bispectral Bilateral System</official_title>
  <sponsors>
